<!--more-->


<p><a href="http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2828/9581046063_ce6b5bd20d_o.jpg"><img src="http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2828/9581046063_ce6b5bd20d_o.jpg"></a><br />
现在好难受，又要无眠吗？</p>
